description: Gumball and Darwin's pranks on Richard get out of hand.
name: The Prank

description: Gumball and Darwin are made fun of by their school mates for wearing martial arts costumes, so Nicole plans to take the costumes away.
name: The Gi

description: Granny Jojo comes for a visit and kisses Gumball on the lips, traumatizing him. Darwin is determined to help Gumball.
name: The Kiss

description: Rachel throws a party and, after blackmail from her brother, lets him and his friends attend on one condition: each of them must bring a date.
name: The Party

description: When Gumball and Darwin buy a video-game from Larry and find out it does not work, they attempt to get a refund.
name: The Refund

description: After Gumball teaches Bobert how to become a real boy, Bobert begins to take over his life.
name: The Robot

description: After not listening properly to instructions given by Miss Simian, Gumball and Darwin must survive in The Forest of Doom.
name: The Picnic

description: Gumball tries desperately to find out Darwin's secret.
name: The Secret

description: Gumball and Darwin learn about honesty from Mr. Small, the school counselor.
name: The Sock

description: Darwin is sent to a government institute for geniuses after scoring highly on an aptitude test.
name: The Genius

description: Gumball and Darwin attempt to save Mr. Robinson's marriage.
name: The Poltergeist

description: When Gumball, Darwin & Anais accidently eat supplements meant for Richard, they become 'men'.
name: The Mustache

description: Gumball goes on a supposed date with his love interest Penny Fitzgerald, only to discover he is actually attending a funeral for Penny's pet.
name: The Date

deck: After a serious accident, Bashir struggles to save the life of Vedek Bareil while Kai Winn concludes a peace treaty with Cardassia. Jake and Nog reluctantly explore the differences between Federation and Ferengi cultures.
name: Life Support

deck: With the sudden death of Grand Nagus Zek, Quark becomes the new leader of the Ferengi Alliance, but he also becomes a target for murder.
name: The Nagus

deck: A fugitive attempts to trade evidence about Odo's people for freedom.
name: Vortex

deck: A runabout carrying Kai Opaka crashes on a planet of eternal war, where it is impossible for the combatants to die.
name: Battle Lines

deck: Chief O'Brien is appointed spiritual leader of a Bajoran village. Meanwhile, Nog and Jake try to help their new friend settle a struggle between two Bajoran villages.
name: The Storyteller

deck: Kira leads the evacuation of a moon which is being converted into a massive powerplant that will render the entire surface uninhabitable, but an old farmer refuses to leave. Back on the station, Jake and Nog set out to turn an inordinate amount of seemingly worthless condiments into profit.
name: Progress

deck: Station residents suddenly find their imaginations are manifested in physical form; a spatial rift threatens to destroy the Bajoran system.
name: If Wishes Were Horses

deck: Batman continues to investigate the mystery behind his impersonator, while a disfigured, crazed Harvey Dent seeks revenge on those that wronged him.
name: Twist

deck: Eph and Abraham team up to kill off the infected.
description: With Nora gone, Eph reluctantly joins Setrakians quest in hopes of gathering enough evidence to warrant a citywide quarantine. Fet encounters the unexpected inside the subway tunnels, and a medical emergency threatens Palmers master plan.
name: Runaways

deck: Scott carries out a dangerous plan. Meanwhile, Malia confronts her past.
name: Time of Death

description: While en route to Ba Sing Se, Korra and Asami manage to escape from their cell, but their attempt to take control of the vessel ends with them crashing in the Si Wong Desert. Meanwhile, in Ba Sing Se, Mako and Bolin are imprisoned while the Red Lotus strikes a deal with Earth Queen for the Avatar. The Red Lotus have no interest in keeping their deal and soon remove the Queen from her office permanently. With the Earth Queen removed, Ba Sing Se devolves into anarchy as Ghazan brings down the citys famed walls.
name: Long Live the Queen

description: In order to get his powers back, Beast Boy returns to nature and finds it much harsher than he expects.
name: Nature

description: Mad Mod steals the youth from Cyborg, Beast Boy, Starfire and Robin, turning them into Raven's favorite type of people: salty codgers. Instead of helping the Titans get their youth back, Raven teaches them how cool old people are.
name: Salty Codgers

description: Finn and Jake's parents hunt an unearthly menace in the woods.
name: Joshua and Margaret Investigations

deck: Searching for a Maquis raider on an unstable moon, Kira is trapped in an expanding crystal formation that threatens to engulf her if Odo cannot set her free. Meanwhile, Nog attempts to persuade a skeptical Commander Benjamin Sisko to write him a letter of recommendation to join Starfleet Academy.
name: Heart of Stone

deck: An ancient Bajoran prophecy of doom complicates the first joint Bajoran, Cardassian, and Federation science mission; an attempt to establish a permanent communications link through the wormhole.
name: Destiny

deck: Grand Nagus Zek has become a philanthropist, and Quark worries that he may have gone insane; Bashir is nominated for a prestigious medical award.
name: Prophet Motive

description:
Magic. This product of fairy-tales was systematized as an actual technology at the dawn of the 21st century.

- Shiba Tatsuya

At about 2030 A.D., the world experience a drastic change change in its climate. A massive cooling occurred resulting to reduction of food supply in a world wide scale. Along with food, energy source dwindled and most often than not fought over. In 2045, World War 3 broke out, which last for 20 years.During this time, the World's population was reduced to about 3 billion, it is of little consolation that a thermonuclear war did not occur.

The Nuclear Holocaust was averted due to the global solidarity of the world's magic technicians. Due to the practical usage of magic over conventional weapons, by the end of the 21st Century, every nation in the world is in a race to develop magicians as a foundation of its power.

Transforming into a demon, Brother will stalk the battlefield. For my sake only.

I wonder how I can ever return such a favor to him?

How can I possibly repay him?

When, as it stands now, even my life itself was a gift from him...

- Shiba Miyuki

First High School April 03, 2095. The School's Matriculation Ceremony rehearsal announcement was over shadowed by the voice of a young female letting out her frustrations. She is frustrated upon the fact that her brother is a Course 2 Student or Weed even though he aced the written exam. For Shiba Miyuki, this is a grave injustice that the school has done to his brother, Shiba Tatsuya. Miyuki continuously air her grievance saying that her brother excels at everything even in magic, at that point, Tatsuya stopped Miyuki as if she is a bout to tell something of a secret that must not be revealed. Tatsuya consoled Miyuki and thanked her for caring so much in his behalf. Miyuki left and Tatsuya wonders the school grounds to kill time. During his stroll, he was passed-by by 2 Course 1 Students or should we say Blooms and criticized him for being early and excited despite being a Weed. He took no heed of it when suddenly, someone approached him and started talking to him. It was a girl, by her uniform, a Course 1 student and she is a upperclassman. She introduced herself as Saegusa Mayumi, First High School's Student Council President. Mayumi has a slender body and long black hair tied with a ribbon at the back of her head. By any other word, she is beautiful and have an air of elegance and pride radiating from her, that is of no surprise as Tatsuya recognized her last name being part of the 10 Master Clan, despite being a Course 1 student, she seems to be friendly and easy to approach. He immediately noticed that she is wearing a C.A.D. or Casting Assistance Device, an item used by magicians to cast magic in a much faster speed. Mayumi was still talking when a student, later to be known as A-chan, came to fetch her as Mayumi being the Student Council President has a role in the upcoming ceremony. Upon hearing this, Tatsuya excused himself and left the two behind.

When the time came for the Matriculation Ceremony to commence, Tatsuya head to the designated building, upon entering, he immediately noticed the rift between Blooms and Weeds as half of the building was occupied by both. He then immediately found himself a seat in the Weed side. Tatsuya was approached by a female student asking if the seats at his side is free. He said yes and another female student follows. The two female students introduced themselves as Shibata Mizuki and Chiba Erika. The Matriculation Ceremony finally starts and Shiba Miyuki was called to say a few words as the representative of the 1st Year Students. After the ceremony, Erika asked Tatsuya if he is free to check the school the school with her and Mizuki. He declined saying that his sister is waiting for him. Mizuki asked if Miyuki was Tatsuya's sister and he said yes and asked why she found out disregarding having last name, Mizuki answered that their aura are similar. Tatsuya is taken a back by this as he worries that his secrets may be revealed.

.
name: Enrollment Part I
